Entries.default: "It's been awfully quiet up top, hasn't it now...?"
"The dirty scugs sure smell ripe, don't they?"
"Then the scratching cried he was thirsty. So I bled his mate to fill his cup."
"Stow your whining! You'll rot in here so long as Brutal Ben wants it."
"You'll get your revenge, says you? I'll wait to see that."
"You sodden lurcher, where're you skulking to?"
